The wait is over: the brand new BetterMe is finally here! We are excited to bring you a completely reinvented app with tons of new content, a beautiful user-friendly design, and new features to help you get your dream body even faster!

- We now offer Journeys, a personalized combination of workouts and nutrition to help you reach your goals; 
- All-new targeted training programs and over 1500 recipes from certified coaches and nutritionists;
- Improved Community with daily tips and articles from the leading professionals;
- Personal Coach to guide you along every step of the way and answer any questions you might have;
- Along with a Water Tracker, daily Progress Graphs, Shopping List, Video Recipes and much more.

BetterMe lets you have the expertise of fitness and diet specialists in the palm of your hand without ever having to hit the gym. No wonder that thousands of satisfied customers have rated the app 5 stars and left enthusiastic reviews on the App Store!

Currently, New BetterMe is available in three languages: English, Chinese, and Russian.

Using the app is easy as 1-2-3!

1. Start off by answering these questions about your wellness:

a) What are your goals? Do you want to lose weight or gain muscle mass and get fit?
b) What is your fitness level?
c) What are your diet and meal preferences?

2. Receive a personalized Weight Loss JOURNEY 

A combination of custom workout and meal plans from BetterMe specially tailored to you will get you on track to meet your weight-loss goals in no time! Make sure to check in with the app daily to stay on track and achieve your desired health and fitness results. 

No special equipment needed, only your dedication and resolve! Enjoy targeted and all-body workouts, and warm-ups and cool-downs to make sure you’re getting the full benefit of exercising!

To compliment the workouts, BetterMe offers a variety of well-balanced and practical meal plans that pay attention to your dietary habits and needs. We also take your allergies and the ingredients you don’t like into account. 
New to healthy eating? We are here for you with hundreds of detailed cooking videos. And with the BetterMe shopping list, it is easy to buy only healthy products every time you shop.

....and also:

- Over 300 pages of educational content on fitness, nutrition and weight loss;
- Instructional workouts videos;
- Tips on proper exercise execution;
- Smart water tracker;
- Daily progress charts;
- Weight logging;
- Reminders and motivating messages to encourage your training and healthy diet.

3. Achieve the results you’ve always dreamed of!

As a BetterMe app user, you can choose the subscription plan that best suits your needs, by considering the workout, the diet, and the costs. Our Premium 1-year subscription plan offers unlimited access to every level of every imaginable workout routine in exchange for a single payment. In addition, 1-week subscription and 1-month are available for users. For your convenience, BetterMe subscriptions are set to automatically renew within the 24-hour period prior to the subscription end date. You can cancel your subscription at any moment in your iTunes account settings but refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the terms. Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable.

BetterMe is integrated with the Health kit, so you can find your activities data in the Health App.

Constructive criticism is always welcome. Our fitness, weight loss and diet specialists, as well as our developers, are constantly working to improve the user experience and cater to a wider range of our customers’ needs.
Contact our client support via support@betterme.tips.

